Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 13:03:05 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 07/48] Add Settings dropdown to select the active backend

BackendSelectorView (a Dropdown mirroring StartupShellView) lists 'Warp
(Default)' + the configured backends and persists the choice via
agent_backends::set_selected on pick. Registered as a 'Default backend' widget
row on the Features settings page. Applies on next launch.
